item.description:
We can set up car pools. We can always meet at Panera in Dedham as a Jumping off point. That time would be 11am SHARP!!!!! It's at least an hour drive to Rockport.WE WILL WAIT NO LONGER THAN 10 MIN. FOR LATE COMERS!!! I suggest Lobster lunch first in groups . This really in the rough. We can sit out on the rustic deck overlooking Folly Cove. There are also sea food plates & seafood rolls. You may bring your own beer or wine. If you're planning on ordering a large lobster please get your order in early! Then we can break up into groups according to various interrests & always set a check in meeting time.

Phone# there is (978) 546-6696.
item.how_to_find_us: Order your meal then find us out on the deck.
item.name: Our Annual Lobster in the Rough
